    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895950/extras/47091a9617deda7451d829cd6f1f9fe1.poster.avif?t=1728987059\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895950/extras/47091a9617deda7451d829cd6f1f9fe1.webm?t=1728987059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895950/extras/47091a9617deda7451d829cd6f1f9fe1.mp4?t=1728987059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895950/extras/3137864f0c1d31afdf6707b8ebc777c8.avif?t=1728987059\" width=600 height=76 /></span><br>心跳度假屋是一个以澳洲的黄金海岸为舞台的恋爱喜剧。<br>在游戏中，你将扮演女主角。原来一心打算渡假的你， 却突然要替爷爷管理度假屋。<br>在管理度假屋的期间，你遇上了四位魅力十足的帅哥，而且他们似乎与你的过去有所联繫!一直被封闭的童年回忆也将渐渐浮上水面。<br>你的选择将会影响故事的发展和角色的好感! 你会选择哪一个?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895950/extras/1eda2e566e00a4d1e942433e509c4d9f.avif?t=1728987059\" width=600 height=76 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895950/extras/4da81dd067b441d7997a187c0f69193f.avif?t=1728987059\" width=600 height=194 /></span><br>全国最大的饮食集团乔山集团的总务兼继任人，，浮夸又温柔的有钱少爷，很喜欢黏着女主角，并且常常出手帮助她。<br>虽然时常面带微笑但却很难让人猜得透他在想什麽，似乎有着伤痛的过去。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895950/extras/f445751551a7a8b7a1b9786d345a625d.avif?t=1728987059\" width=600 height=194 /></span><br>有点毒舌的运动男子，很喜欢欺负女主角同时又很照顾她。<br>除了是剑击运动员, 还有另外一个神秘身份。此外，卞义似乎千方百计不想女主角回忆以前的事...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895950/extras/1b483b978dcbf25123e9b5b9d96c3672.avif?t=1728987059\" width=600 height=194 /></span><br>人畜无害的小天使，同时也时风摩万千少女的天才魔术师。<br>入住当天就向女主角求婚。有如一只可爱的小狗狗，对女主千依百顺。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895950/extras/8d86e15499dbd758fa5416b301a176d0.avif?t=1728987059\" width=600 height=194 /></span><br>拥有多重身份的白然，非布里斯之家住客，可是却又频频在女主角身边出现。<br>因为某个原因而用着双重身份与女主角见面，总是在女主角有危险时出来保护她。<br>虽然长相可爱但却有着超强的战斗力。<br>突然展开的同居生活! 一边经营民宿一边谈恋爱!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895950/extras/ae04cacfb9e6ca58cc55e2325a0488c3.poster.avif?t=1728987059\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895950/extras/ae04cacfb9e6ca58cc55e2325a0488c3.webm?t=1728987059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895950/extras/ae04cacfb9e6ca58cc55e2325a0488c3.mp4?t=1728987059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895950/extras/8ac3a830700fd60d7d97adc8ef30cb55.avif?t=1728987059\" width=600 height=76 /></span><br>~四段截然不同的恋爱体验, 满满的心动剧情<br>~你的选择将会影响故事的发展以及与角色的关係<br>~多个结局<br>~心跳加速的CG图库",
